Package: xadr
Type: Package
Title: R Bindings for the XAD Automatic Differentiation Library
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alberto", "Robles", email = "alrobles@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Xcelerit Computing Ltd", role = c("cph"), comment = "XAD C++ library"))
Description: Provides R bindings for the XAD high-performance automatic
    differentiation (AD) library. Supports both forward (tangent-linear) mode
    and adjoint (reverse) mode differentiation of scalar functions. Forward mode
    is efficient for computing derivatives with respect to a single input, while
    adjoint mode computes the full gradient vector in a single backward sweep.
    Includes bindings for over 40 differentiable mathematical functions.
License: AGPL-3
URL: https://github.com/alrobles/xad-r
BugReports: https://github.com/alrobles/xad-r/issues
